The evidence with the title 'Romney haunted by liberal past | PolitiFact ' says Dec 11, 2007  ... In november 2007 , during an appearance on MSNBC's "Morning Joe" program, Giuliani accused Romney of once saying "he would be to the left of Teddy Kennedy on gay rights." Then Giuliani added a more potent charge among GOP voters. He said Romney "didn't even support Ronald Reagan.". 
